\s Msafiri ulie njiani 
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Msafiri uliye njiani, watamani nyumba ya babako. Sikiliza nyimbo za \bd*\bd Mbingu\bd*\bd ni\bd*\bd ! U karibu sana kufikako. \bd*
